query: Could you define the word : tariff.

results.title: TARIFF Definition & Meaning
results.snippet: 1. a : a schedule of duties imposed by a government on imported or in some countries exported goods b : a duty or rate of duty imposed in such a schedule.

results.title: Tariff
results.snippet: A tariff is a tax or duty imposed by a national government, customs territory, or supranational union on imports (or, exceptionally, exports) of goods.

results.title: What Is a Tariff and Why Are They Important?
results.snippet: A tariff is a tax imposed by one country on the goods and services imported from another country.
